<bibRefCitation id="1B694B064F3DFFE8F0C2FBA8FE406C7F" author="Moure, J. S. &amp; P. D. Hurd, Jr." box="[200,469,1091,1115]" pageId="16" pageNumber="15" refId="ref14866" refString="Moure, J. S., and P. D. Hurd, Jr. 1987. An annotated catalog of the halictid bees of the Western Hemisphere (Halictidae). Smithsonian Institution Press; Washington, D. C. 405 p." type="book" year="1987">Moure and Hurd 1987</bibRefCitation>
